        walkthrough = '1. Mano-Amano is located at the Frontier Station. Speak to him to start the quest.\n2. Travel to (I-8) of Yorcia Weald, directly west of the Cirdas Caverns Entrance, and click on the ??? among the numbing blossoms. You will obtain the Fistful of numbing soil.\n   - You can get there fast from Bivouac #2 and going north.\n   - There may be an impassable bush blocking the path. Simply wait until 21:00 game time to proceed.\n3. Return to Mano-Amano for your reward.',
