        fame = 'Adoulin',
        fame_level = '1',
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. After registering with the Pioneers\' Coalition, zone and wait for a game day change before returning to the Pioneers\' Coalition for a cutscene.\n2. Proceed to the eastern half of (G-8) in Ceizak Battlegrounds and click the Earthen Mound for another cutscene.\n   - Located just south of Bivouac #2\n3. Head southwest to (E-10) and enter the Sih Gates.\n4. Once inside, head west to (E-6) and click on the Foreboding Presence for another cutscene.\n5. Click on it again to spawn the NM Fomor Pioneer.\n   - The NM may cast Cure IV / Cure V on players / pets occasionally, healing them for ~600 HP.\n   - Fomor Pioneer is highly evasive and has approximately 10,000 HP.\n   - Was a simple duo for DNC/NIN and SAM/DNC\n   - Trusts make this fight trivial for solo players.\n6. Click on the Foreboding Presence one last time after defeating the NM for another cutscene and the Reive unity Key Item.\n7. Head back to the Pioneers\' Coalition for another Cutscene and reward.',
        notes = nil,
