        start_npc = 'Jorin',
        start_zone = 'Western Adoulin',
        start_pos = 'J-4',
        description = 'A lone fisherman will lose his battle with the big one unless you carry his trusty harpoon to the Inventors\' Coalition for repair.',
        reward = '500 Experience Points\n300 Bayld',
        fame = 'Adoulin',
        fame_level = '1',
        title = nil,
        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = nil,
        next = {'Fertile Ground'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Jorin in Western Adoulin (J-4) near the Adoulin Waterfront to obtain a [Key Item] Broken harpoon.\n2. Speak with Shipilolo at (J-9) outside the Inventors\' Coalition to obtain the [Key Item] Extravagant harpoon.\n3. Return to Jorin to complete the Quest.',
        notes = nil,
    },
    ['The Secret to Success'] = {
        id = 127,
        start_npc = 'Behsa Alehgo',
        start_zone = 'Eastern Adoulin',
        start_pos = 'J-8',
        description = 'Erfimia is convinced that there is no way a run-of-the-mill exorcist like Robertioux could pull off such an incredible feat without a clandestine training regime, and thus wants you to discover his secret.',
        reward = '1000 Bayld',
        fame = 'Adoulin',
        fame_level = '3',
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = {'Eye of the Beholder'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Behsa Alehgo at (J-7/J-8) in Eastern Adoulin at the priory (near the castle) for a cutscene.\n2. Head to the Scouts\' Coalition and talk to Wegellion at (F-9) for a cutscene.\n   - If he gives the option to hand over the hat, do that then talk again to get the cutscene.\n3. Head to the Frontier Station at (J-8) in Yorcia Weald and talk to Emjook-Renook for a cutscene.\n4. Emjook-Renook said he lost his Unblemished pioneer\'s badge at one of the following locations (J-8), (H-9), and (I-8).\n5. Check the Suspicious Places at (J-8), (H-9), and (I-8) to obtain the Unblemished pioneer\'s badge.  Only one of them will have the item.\n   - (J-8): South west corner of J-8.\n     - Head south east from the Frontier Station into J-9.\n     - You\'ll see a bunch of Bronzecap and when you reach the fork, take the path to the right (S, not SE) until you see Saptrap.\n     - Turn right, and then right again, passing some Twitherym, and that will put you into the bottom left corner of J-8. The target is behind a tree.\n     - A bush (used to) possibly obstruct this from 00:00 - 6:00.\n   - (H-9): South west corner at H-9.\n     - Head north west from Bivouac #2.\n     - A Colonization Reive will be in the way.\n   - (I-8): Located in the field of Numbing Blossoms towards the south side of (I-8).\n     - Head east from the Suspicious Place at H-9 (NW from #2) and go north-east towards the Cirdas Caverns entrance.\n     - A bush may obstruct this except from 21:00 - 3:00.\n6. Return to Emjook-Renook for a cutscene.\n7. Speak with Behsa Alehgo for the final cutscene and your reward.',
        notes = nil,
    },
    ['The Silent Forest'] = {
        id = 144,
        start_npc = 'Levil',
        start_zone = 'Western Adoulin',
        start_pos = 'E-8',
        description = 'Living in harmony with the forest requires the assistance of the avatar Siren. Head to Escha - Ru\'Aun and look for clues regarding her disappearance.',
        reward = 'Choice of one:\nPact with Siren\n10,000 Bayld',
        fame = 'Adoulin',
        fame_level = nil,
        title = 'Eternal Communer',
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {
            'The Light Within',
            'A Rhapsody for the Ages',
        },
        next = {'Winds of Eternity'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Levil in the Pioneers\' Coalition (E-8) for a cutscene to begin the Quest.\n2. Speak with Ploh Trishbahk at (K-9) in Eastern Adoulin for another cutscene.\n   - At this point the Quest will now show in your log.\n3. Go to Escha - Ru\'Aun and examine the blue ??? at (H-10) at the top of the stairs to the left of the entrance for a cutscence. You will receive [Key Item] Inert geomancy bell.\n4. Return to Ploh Trishbahk for another cutscene.\n5. Meet Arciela, Ygnas, and Darrcuiln in Kamihr Drifts at (H-5), and examine the Alpine Trail for a cutscene. This will take you into a zone named Mount Kamihr.\n   - This is the very most northern-middle point on the map.\n     - The fastest way there is take Bivouac #3, go into the northern tunnel and follow the left wall, always heading north.\n   - Selecting the options "Lifestream" then "Communion" continues the conversation in a constructive way.\n6. Venture to the Crag closest to your home Nation and click the Ergon Locus ??? located beneath the stairs leading up to the Telepoint to obtain  Fistful of familiar soil and view a cutscene.\n   - If you are in the middle of Dances with Luopans and have not received a  Luopan, you need to turn the  Fistful of familiar soil into a [Key Item] Luopan first, then go get another [Key Item] Fistful of familiar soil for the cutscene.\n   - Cannot be obtained while possessing [Key Item] Holla crystal of gales, [Key Item] Dem crystal of dunes, or [Key Item] Mea crystal of flames from Treasures of the Earth of the same type.\n     - e.g. having the Holla crystal prevents obtaining the Fistful of familiar soil from the Crag of Holla Ergon Locus ???.\n7. Enter Leafallia for a cutscene.\n8. Examine the glowing spot Drifting Feather at (H-7) for another cutscene.\n9. Examine the Drifting Feather again to enter a BCNM.\n   - Your opponent will be Siren Prime.\n     - The fight is Content Level 119.\n     - Trusts may be used in the fight.\n     - Siren absorbs Light Skillchains.\n     - Siren has a move that can Charm.\n10. Upon defeating Siren, a cutscene will begin where you will be able to choose your reward.\n----\n11. See also: Testimonial Discussion Page.',
        notes = nil,
    },
