            {name = '[Key Item] Holla crystal of gales', count = 1},
            {name = '[Key Item] Dem crystal of dunes', count = 1},
            {name = '[Key Item] Mea crystal of flames', count = 1},
            {name = '[Key Item] Pale azure cloth', count = 1},
            {name = '[Key Item] Treatise on azimuth clothcraft', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Sylvie at Western Adoulin Waterfront (I-5) Waypoint #9 as Geomancer to begin the quest.\n   - Turning in the Key Item [Key Item]Crystallized lifestream essence to Wescolina allows for the activation of this quest.\n     - Acquiring all of the relic armor pieces is not required.\n2. Go to Morimar Basalt Fields (J-6) northeast of bivouac #2 and check the Ergon Locus ??? for a cutscene.\n3. Go to (G/H-7) and ascend the Scalable Area near the NW side of the Hot Spring. Go directly east to (H-6/7) and check the ??? (at the base of the cliff overhang, beneath the ergon locus) for a cutscene.\n   - If you don\'t have [Key Item]"Climbing" it is possible to die, Tractor, and Raise twice down from bivouac #5.\n4. Return to Sylvie. She will offer you the choice of three challenges.\n   - Choosing [Key Item]Holla crystal of gales corresponds to a level 109 solo fight in La Theine Plateau.\n   - Choosing [Key Item]Dem crystal of dunes corresponds to a level 125 solo fight in Konschtat Highlands.\n   - Choosing the blank option will give you the [Key Item]Mea crystal of flames. This corresponds to a level 135 solo Geomancer fight in Tahrongi Canyon.',
        notes = nil,
    },
