        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Inmot-Pinmot at Bivouac #2 to accept the quest.\n2. Head west towards the beach (with a tree reive), but instead of crossing the tree, head south along the coast until you reach the secret beach at (J-11).\n3. Examine the Ergon Locus to obtain a Fistful of pristine sand.\n4. Return to Inmot-Pinmot for your reward.',
